    "result": {"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoxMDQ0","title":"The Perfect Drift","slug":"the-perfect-drift","excerpt":"<p>With winter steelhead fishing upon us, I think about side drifting along the banks of my favorite coastal river, the Trinity River. All through these cold winter days, most of my time is spent fly fishing. I still look forward to my days spent gear fishing (fishing with conventional tackle) in search of winter chrome.â€¦ <a href=\"/the-perfect-drift/\">Read More &raquo;</a></p>\n","content":"<p>With winter <a  href=\"/tag/steelhead/\">steelhead</a> fishing upon us, I think about side drifting along the banks of my favorite coastal river, the <a  href=\"/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/category/locations/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/tag/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/fishing-news/trinity-river/\">Trinity River</a></a></a></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All through these cold winter days, most of my time is spent fly fishing. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>I still look forward to my days spent gear fishing (fishing with conventional tackle) in search of winter chrome. But fly fishing is a super interesting style of angling that allows me to look at a river differently. With conventional gear, at times, I can be limited. Fly fishing, from a boat, provides a ton of options opening up water we would typically skip when using conventional gear. Let&#8217;s talk options!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What weight to use?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Each river you fish may have preferred &#8220;weight&#8221; used by the local fishermen. Sometimes the most important component in the angling process isn&#8217;t limited to the hot fly or lure. It&#8217;s the &#8220;weight&#8221; or split shot that gets the fly/lure in front of the fish that all too often goes ignored. Use the wrong amount of weight and our chances are reduced.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some fishermen find it difficult to try something new or to be new at a technique this can limit your progress as a fisherman and make things difficult. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>I mostly fish the upper <a  href=\"/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/category/locations/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/tag/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/fishing-news/trinity-river/\">Trinity River</a></a></a></a> in Trinity County. Located in Northern California. The <a  href=\"/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/category/locations/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/tag/trinity-river/\"><a  href=\"/fishing-news/trinity-river/\">Trinity River</a></a></a></a> is one of the best <a  href=\"/tag/steelhead/\">steelhead</a> rivers on the entire western coast of the USA!.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><span class=\"wp-image-1077 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/b95e4/image2-scaled.jpg 256w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/1779b/image2-scaled.jpg 512w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/87945/image2-scaled.jpg 1024w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/6afe2/image2-scaled.jpg 1536w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/7a411/image2-scaled.jpg 2048w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/bb9a8/image2-scaled.jpg 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/b95e4/image2-scaled.jpg 256w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/1779b/image2-scaled.jpg 512w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/87945/image2-scaled.jpg 1024w,\n/static/5f9d5210793a8580c08aaccd5e5e4834/6afe2/image2-scaled.jpg 1536w,\n/static/5f9d52